Place all gems into corresponding subdirectories, that have been specifically prepared, i.e.
it this folder here -- concurrent ruby etc. have been added to avoid automatic native extension building

## UPDATED
git clone https://github.com/ruby-concurrency/concurrent-ruby

bundle update
install openjdk8-jdk (for javac)
install jruby
export JRUBY_HOME=/usr/share/jruby
rake gem

